qgisprocess (development version)

qgisprocess 0.1.0

CRAN release: 2023-08-17

  • Initial CRAN submission.
  • While the package has been incubating for a few years as a development version, quite a few namespace changes were made in 2023 before preparing the first CRAN release (#153). Since the package probably had a substantial user community before these changes, old function names still work but these are deprecated. They will be dropped at a later stage.
